.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F001152_fcfbf441da8960f632e8994faeeb73b1.png&h=30752a3b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幅圖正確﹐但紅字係錯<br />\n<br />\n本身上年因為匯價而賺左三億﹐如果今年個匯價不變﹐咁理論上都會賺得番呢幾億<br />\n但就係因為人仔跌所以係18年變成蝕三億﹐咁未一來一回係無左6億"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝"},{"pid":"ace6797f03376788ab74b14a8e51eb7874e4e634","tid":788342,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34ef6812f7911f4adcf21b4c31185182151c09a","tid":788342,"uid":153977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"現價仲入得過？"},{"pid":"9f1023efa7505afb1d67d62923874682f8099e4f","tid":788342,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現價仲入得過？</blockquote><br />\n3未必真係入得過。"},{"pid":"739a35c87f4af703381b40adb9c3bb835b94216e","tid":788342,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T03:48:20.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}